    "body": "Those are all good suggestions. All the translations will be cleaned up, renamed (for those that need it), and old strings removed. Adding tokens to translation strings is a great idea, I'll update the translate functions and any existing strings to use string literals for variables like amounts or addresses\r\n\r\nI'm not sure if there's anyway to properly highlight every translated string. If we were using just `translate` everywhere, a class could be appended onto the parent text's parent `<span />`, but then we'd have a bunch of extra `<span />`'s everywhere  ",
